# ENTITY::IS_ENTITY_A_MISSION_ENTITY

## Summary
Checks if the entity has been created by script

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Will return false if the entity has been set as no longer needed.
